definitions.definition: An organelle , found in the cells of green plants and in photosynthetic algae , where photosynthesis takes place, characterized by a high concentration of chlorophyll and two membranes.

main_definition: ( cytology ) An organelle , found in the cells of green plants and in photosynthetic algae , where photosynthesis takes place, characterized by a high concentration of chlorophyll and two membranes.
